  <條文>
    <條號>Article 47</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[What is termed a program confiscation as stipulated in Article 45-2 of this Act refers to the tape or disc on which a radio/television program, advertisement or a videorecording program is recorded.
]]></條文內容>
